data.description: If space is what you're looking for, say hello to your new home! This gorgeous two story 4bedroom brick home has over 3,400 sq ft!! Live comfortable in the space that you and your family needs. Featuring an open floor plan, spacious kitchen, two living areas, eat in kitchen and over sized pantry, this home has it all! Don't worry about buying kitchen appliances! Included you will find stainless steel appliances, including refrigerator! ALL bedrooms upstairs and NO carpet!! Enjoy the huge deck, perfect for bbq days & hangouts! Shed available for extra storage!
